{"tid":573318,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔平時會唔會寫簡體字？","createTime":"2018-02-26T11:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T02:21:30.000Z","uid":51129,"like":3,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a41ebc7881b65d25f1734710d32001525663c8d8","tid":573318,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"其實簡體字真係好方便，筆劃少寫得快<br />\n<br />\n尤其連登咁多中學雞，考試嘅時候要爭分奪秒，寫簡體字就係一大便利<br />\n<br />\n而繁體字根本就係反人類，好似「憂鬱」呢兩隻字，加埋就黎五十劃都有，痴撚線點撚樣寫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實文字黎講，真係冇乜野係比方便更加重要<br />\n<br />\n就好似連登仔平時上網打字噉，啲「咗」呀「嘅」呀嗰啲字漏哂口字邊都唔會理，屌你速成要㩒成十幾頁點撚樣打呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d2612daf686ec8d2d1536839de28bbb60978ca","tid":573318,"uid":134474,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:11:40.000Z","msg":"Block 漏你條仆街五毛添"},{"pid":"fabbb9082ae4850e4245093a6f2a4a2dbfcbfda5","tid":573318,"uid":51129,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"其實嗰班打個「嘅」字都嫌麻煩嘅垃圾有咩資格屌人寫簡體字?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3b40a106f76c35feb6965f882d4b889f654d0f","tid":573318,"uid":51129,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"做乜事咁多負皮？連登仔唔係不嬲覺得方便係重要過寫啱隻字架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4103d732c0eee3b04904b4e150d60041675c9d0","tid":573318,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"文字有好多用法<br />\n如果為方便比自己睇唔反對<br />\n畫錯別字都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n但係寫formal野就唔可以<br />\n特別係香港公司同政府就一定唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42db6d62698a5dd7d42059b5ade0e462fd70f48e","tid":573318,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d4103d732c0eee3b04904b4e150d60041675c9d0","tid":573318,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci